<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Temporary Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333333;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .tempPassword {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #1e88e5;
      background: #f0f8ff;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      display: inline-block;
      border-radius: 6px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }
    p {
      color: #555555;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 15px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      background: #1e88e5;
      color: #fff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
    <p>Here is your <strong>temporary password</strong> for login to <%= settings.siteName %>:</p>
    <div class="tempPassword"><%= tempPassword %></div>
    <p>This password is valid for a limited time. Please log in and change your password immediately for security.</p>
    <p>If you did not request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

    <p><strong>Need help?</strong> Join our official WhatsApp channel for updates:<br>
      <a href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/HlDnLNWQsws88ZbyNTdYdN" class="btn" target="_blank">Join WhatsApp Channel</a>
    </p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>
    Team <%= settings.siteName %></p>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= settings.siteName %>. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
